; exit-truth-dep.fk -- fixture for src-exit-truth-band.fk: INTENTIONALLY not
; standalone-compilable. It calls xt-prov-one but carries NO "; preludes:" line
; of its own, so the speculative per-unit image compile diagnoses one
; unresolved call, while the root's flat chain (prov before dep) resolves it.
; This is the exact shape that made 8 printed errors exit 0 on 2026-07-17
; (form/form-stdlib/satsang.fk under learn/satsang-oracle.fk).
(defn xt-dep-two () (xt-prov-one))
